139
00:10:14.450 --> 00:10:16.890
Datanglah, ke tempatku sekarang.

140
00:10:17.989 --> 00:10:19.020
Tidak.

141
00:10:20.619 --> 00:10:23.430
Maukah kau datang kemari?

142
00:10:23.690 --> 00:10:25.430
